Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…要迟到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已经放暑假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊呀 理音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 不要捣蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都说不行了啦 很痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前略 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不肖顽弟上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}自暑假初始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已然大事不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}尚存理性与否
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}实……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无自知矣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在！怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这摄影机是买的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那看起来还真是古旧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在家里的仓库找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想…大概是逝世的爷爷留下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知怎的…挺中意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐呐 该怎么用啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}装上这卷胶卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后对好镜头的焦距
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后按下快门就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太近了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从暑假的第一天起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就变得“坦率”多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才…才没那种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在干嘛呢 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在练柔韧性吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 让我们开始快快乐乐的电影制作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐 海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天要拍什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}负责剧本的是柠檬学姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的份已经写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的份？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的拍片风格是香港式的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一天要拍的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那天的早上决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不是到哪儿说哪儿吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}换好衣服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好棒！很合适啊 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这衣服是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起来好像斥资不菲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我拜托学校的COSPLAY社团和我们合作了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们还有这种社团吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会不会很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.11,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an9}女主人公降落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.11,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an9}与少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.11,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an9}相遇 然后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天要拍的内容是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女主角第一次与那个男孩相遇的场景哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}言情剧啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞不好很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顺带一提 女主角的设定是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真新潮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才穿那身衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}降落到地球之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女主角与地球人的少年命运般的邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}台词全部即兴完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剩下的交给导演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是乱来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那谁演地球人的少年啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我得顾着摄影机 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那只能是我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我觉得很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定很合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是打算在后台帮手的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要会临机应变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对 拍摄现场可是活的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说得很懂似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什么不行的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能和贵月学姐这么漂亮的人演对手戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定会成为一生难忘的回忆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的人生到这就走到顶点了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这…一副乐在其中的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才没这回事~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要演外星人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没…什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 准备好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…那就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}准备 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…这里就是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开发等级F的边境行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由于这颗星球对宇宙开发才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}载人登陆的…只有被称作月球的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这颗星球的卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这台词…挺真实的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然有点结结巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下来 石垣同学上镜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我是因为一些缘由而来到这个星球的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找…找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}变成已经见过的设定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直在注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}事实上是外星人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后我是黑衣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(722,660)}Men in black
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}黑…黑衣人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 石垣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 一不小心就太起劲儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}演对手戏的…死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样…好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐…即兴演得真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知不觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…现在是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为电影的内容改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在等柠檬学姐改剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是女主角展开逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后和黑衣人之间激烈的追逐战啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里…怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这前面还有池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 学姐你上次不是提到过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有树有池塘…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是个没什么特别之处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那该怎样找呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也对呢 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就是想去那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我挑选了一些相似的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但好像不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我还会再找的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这…你这…你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜 把饮料拿给一夏学姐他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我之前就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 你是不是知道我的心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有目共睹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么时候开始…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在支持我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}毕竟是青梅竹马嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}交到女朋友要告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会支持你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这恐怕…不太可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很痛啊 北原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一时发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再次开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为了逃脱追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女主角回到了宇宙船上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那里和伙伴会合了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}伙伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谁来演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这孩子的设定是宇宙船的生体终端
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请多关照了 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐 准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都搞不清楚谁才是导演了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摄像机 准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}准备 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 有追兵赶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥的仇就由我来报!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 石垣同学 理音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你干嘛擅自跑进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼 这或许是演员的自我修养吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你修养太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…接下来要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从现在开始想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有住的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对…对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那要来我家住吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是一个人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}家里有很多空房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:10:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢 真的十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}终于回到主线了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说 我怎么就成演员了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而不是摄影师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还能和一夏学姐演对手戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这家伙 难道说是故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}变成和海人演对手戏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到头来还是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你觉得今后 那两个人会有什么发展？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么 学姐觉得怎么发展好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…我觉得只要能幸福就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到头来 导演和摄影师都由柠檬学姐包下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下来会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思我先去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这澡洗的真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么 明天也要拍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然都看柠檬学姐安排
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐吩咐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要尽可能多拍一些女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}渐渐融入地球生活的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这种场景就别拍进去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是在说电影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人如果知道了女主角的真实身份会怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那该由柠檬学姐去想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只会单纯觉得“好厉害啊”这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是说那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“能不能把我也带去宇宙呢”什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有规定限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你觉得和不同星球的人在一起也没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 只要不会射出什么奇怪的液体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才没那种东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也没什么不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是不会在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是 谷川家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 美樱 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然今天不拍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}毕竟下着这么大的雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到时再联系咯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在聊什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月学姐 已经习惯这里的生活了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 已经相当习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是啊 学姐有时挺怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟然做出巧克力味的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算是吧 略显微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 得去买菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么 回去时绕路去趟超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说起来 纸巾也快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}洗涤剂也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那也顺便去趟药店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请问是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}午安 妈妈叫我拿过来给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}芜菁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 有这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为这房子很旧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等放晴了我去屋顶看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起 我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事 这种事不多见嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀 谷川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请便请便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃 这话也不该由我来说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 不介意的话 一起吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 柑菜 出门了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明下着这么大的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是啊 还拎走了咱家里的芜菁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我女儿真是个奇怪的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 等她回来请告诉她我打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 那就先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}夹芜菁的…三明治？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难得嘛 就用这个试着做了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什么地方搞错了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然有点像烤馅饼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.83,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}把面团擀成薄皮 包入豆沙或蔬菜馅 在铁板上烤制的食品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}连葡萄柚盖饭我都克服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已经没什么能阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请不要那么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又在拍吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为说要我多拍点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同学也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}自然的聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你说要“自然”也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同学有兄弟姐妹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是独生子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…从小就常和哲朗一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒没觉得寂寞什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你和石垣同学认识这么久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他就像个傻弟弟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我倒是觉得石垣同学更像哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是因为他个子高你才这么觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那学姐有没有兄弟姐妹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有姐姐还有妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来是三姐妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们家属于女生多的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以到这里来感觉挺新鲜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来家里有个男生…是这种感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果把海人比作家人 那像是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像是弟弟吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…是有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过海人有时候也挺可靠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么说呢…说不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶…听不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是…刚才那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐是来这里留学的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那打算在这儿待多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是半年呢…还是一年？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我说了这种多余的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯嗯 没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么会出说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样多惹人厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多过分…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不像样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不可爱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是美樱说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去海人家了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这不是挺有勇气的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是没去就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能融进去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}心里就像是有疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他们只是说话我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我讨厌这么想的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去告白咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海啊…还没和学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么可能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果被拒绝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定会很尴尬的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是因为这样而不愉快…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下来大家还要一起拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是变成那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我怎么还能去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也一定会很受困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就这样什么也不做的 继续烦恼下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你没喜欢上谁就根本不知道我的感受！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎 你根本不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也说得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}停了停了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个啊 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会和往常一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和大家一起开开心心的拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍好了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在校园文化节之类上放…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会做回平常那个谷川柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来 走吧 哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个时候…发生了那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都不曾去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无论是谷川的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还是哲郎的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有北原的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都不曾去知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我被某个想法牵绊着…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…学姐终会消失的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拉我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我胳膊快没劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}生命反应？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这么晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这么晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说你给我从玄关进来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说吧 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川她今天来我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:22:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢……雾岛海人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是冲绳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是冲绳啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很刺激啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 很诱人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 真受不了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:21.91,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}我曾一直追寻 喜欢上你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:30.10,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}若要为它饰上最合适的言语 那大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:36.79,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}当我悄然发觉时 心绪早已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:45.29,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}紧系于你 愈缠愈紧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:52.81,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&HCD6A1D&\t(2864,3156,\3c&H0090FF)}若我不曾踌躇 对你说出那句话来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:58.94,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&HDB6CEB&\t(2551,3000,\3c&H77BD3E)}你已经不哭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:02.93,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}越过流云的浮影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:05.58,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}绘出想你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:13.86,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}在弥漫着盛夏的芳香之中 无数次浮现出你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.86,0:23:17.55,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}是谁曾触及那所谓轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:22.31,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}像夏日午后滴咚下落的雷阵雨那般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:30.24,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}点上一抹新色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:07.75,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}海风轻拂过你的脸颊 可你却只是默不作声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:15.42,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}其实是好想亲抚你的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:23.02,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}好像被轻吻了一下 那宛若梦境的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:30.98,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}如同微风晃过 现实的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:38.53,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}看似随意的话语中 却照出日常的璀璨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:45.20,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}庞若何时一同看过的电影那般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:53.88,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}不论季节如何流转 也依然等待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:02:01.26,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}像是微焦的胶片一般 夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:09.73,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,300)}不曾消却的预感总刺痛着我 而我终越过 那个在镜头后怯怯望着的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:19.57,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\fad(300,500)}只因我一直紧握着那双手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:33.00,STAFF,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}本字幕由白月字幕组和DHR动研联合制作
